page.title: 12TRADE IN KEYINGHAM
page.content: Ottringham being the smaller village has only two general grocers shops, a post office and a hairdressers. There are several businesses, ie:- Plumbers and electricians, Painter and Decorator, Butcher, Agricultural Suppliers, Agricultural Machinery Suppliers, Accountant. Villagers can obtain most food stuff without having to travel although some prefer to do so. Keyingham has more shops, two small supermarkets, general grocers, butchers, hairdressers, ladies and childrens clothes shop, wool and haberdasherie, bakers shop, green grocers, two newsagents/sweets shops and an electrical shop. Apart from the shops there are several businesses, ie:- Engineering Works, Builders, Gravel Pitts, Garage, Market Gardeners.
